{"tid":1635044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[流動連儂牆] 紅+黑=黨鐵！","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T17:48:36.000Z","uid":255092,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e508742c240e4f0a8a1c0800f571c8c8c3d0ac90","tid":1635044,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"既然大家都估到黨鐵唔敢得罪唔返工會死既香港人同商家佬<br />\n聽日一定開得返嘅話<br />\n閒日多乘客唔方便幫佢<strong>裝修</strong><br />\n咁幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">裝飾</span></strong>下都得掛？<br />\n點解從來冇人幫黨鐵裝飾？<br />\n一齊嚟睇下以下示範：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/1520842863_7ff5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F1520842863_7ff5.jpg&h=a97bb8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mtr.bj.cn/Upload/image/20150305/20150305161041_0312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.bj.cn%2FUpload%2Fimage%2F20150305%2F20150305161041_0312.jpg&h=c48e55fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hongkonghustle.com/wp-content/SonyMTRad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkonghustle.com%2Fwp-content%2FSonyMTRad.jpg&h=cf527b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果每一部黨鐵列車都充滿住我地既文宣圖<br />\n<strong>咁咪即刻有一千幾百塊流動連儂牆囉！</strong><br />\n<br />\n以下係個人推薦：<br />\n1. 揀d冇幕門嘅車站，企響月台度幫每一架埋站嘅列車裝飾，一個鐘就可以裝飾好幾十架喇！<br />\n2. 有minion/food panda捉嘅就即刻跳上車，列車內籠都幫佢裝飾下，再跑去另一車卡避下站職員捕，然後去第個站繼續<br />\n3. 如果係輕鐵就仲方便，所有站/車廂任裝飾唔嬲！<br />\n4. 我覺得用噴字會快手d難d發現，倒模噴又得，文宣圖就要耐d同易比人清唔推薦"},{"pid":"eb36ab87cbe028e0478e29242d0e4be89c3e0323","tid":1635044,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"過人權法之前等勇武有d野做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac7c5fa947a4efbfffb1e1091274c9be97578c7","tid":1635044,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"和理非之中又帶少少勇武<br />\n簡直係和理勇既新手任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343e4f19012b9842e5f8fcb2f8e1900fad64edc2","tid":1635044,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"27d6f4592fbdffa3de760aa7350fcd4642b2565b","tid":1635044,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"紅黑紅紅黑"},{"pid":"20f5b35220d620a739c1e7da0049dcfa258c6fa2","tid":1635044,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"連儂列車"},{"pid":"1c97699fffecdf6369c8493812ab1c43328652ad","tid":1635044,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid":"cd9e0a046ff8bd5879f1bdab13979da7b937d075","tid":1635044,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"一諗起黨鐵呢頭清完d裝修<br />\n果頭又一大堆裝飾就心情舒暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf85e9b4bb36666e31ee138d63d615012b99275","tid":1635044,"uid":255092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"黨鐵一日唔重回正軌<br />